      {
        "type": "post",
        "description": "At the beginning of this year, I created this \"Fireside chat with CUHK IE Alumni\" (https://spoti.fi/34XeJaz) 🎙️ #podcast series (mostly in Cantonese), in which I chat with graduates of Department of Information Engineering, CUHK and get to know their career development and experience after graduation.\n\nNow half a year has passed and I have recorded 14 episodes 🚀. I must say that this is one of the best things that I have ever started. Through this project, I have connected to alumni working in different locations, companies and professions, I have learnt about the responsibilities, challenges and fun of various roles in the technology industry. I am also deeply impressed by my fellow alumni's passion in technology and their eagerness to acquire new skills and knowledge to overcome challenges in their career.\n\nI have received messages from different people showing support and appreciation to this podcast series, and the number of people listening to the series has been increasing steadily, which are very encouraging! I look forward to chatting with more fellow alumni and bringing insights and advice to students and fresh graduates.\n\nI would also like to thank all of the guests who contributed greatly to this podcast series so far! Wing Chung, Yu Peng, Cho Yiu (Michael) Ng, Marco Leung, Kin Leung, Kevin Cheung, Terry Chan, Ellie Liu, Ka Lung Ng, Francis Chong, Calvin Chan, Ka tim Chu, Gloria Chan, Yandy Tse.",
